I have selected a number between 1 to 100. Now you try to guess it!

Enter your guess: 50
Your guess is too high!

Enter your guess: 25
Your guess is too low!

Enter your guess: 37
Your guess is too low!

Enter your guess: 43
Your guess is too high!

